Alex Mitchley  Johannesburg - An out of control truck tore through several properties before crashing into a home in Kempton Park, on the East Rand, on Saturday afternoon. ER24 spokesperson Werner Vermaak said the driver had apparently lost control of the vehicle and veered off the road before crashing through three properties, and eventually into the house. No one in the home was injured, however, the truck driver sustained minor injuries.   24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  